column5:
Poka is a young and dynamic company that offers great opportunities for personal and professional growth. In collaboration with his/her peers, the Cloud Developer will be responsible for creating, enhancing and maintaining the technological services and infrastructures that allow Poka to offer a quality product to its customers. Whether it's using technologies like AWS, Cloud Development Kit (CDK) or a variety of SaaS products, the team is always on the lookout to use only the best of the best. You will need to be open-minded and versatile to meet the demands of the industry. You will be directly involved in the success of this high potential company.

Join the Infrastructure team

Poka is a SaaS company that has adopted a Cloud First model from the start. In collaboration with your peers and mentor, you will join a team that is driven by innovation and will give you the opportunity to share your ideas and put them into practice quickly. In addition, your tasks will be primarily development focused, rather than operational, allowing you to have hands-on experience in a real cloud infrastructure team.

You will be responsible for:

Create, enhance and maintain Cloud infrastructure;
Collaborate with the various development teams (backend, frontend, iOS, Data, etc.);
Participate in the evolution of the technological environment based on recent innovations;
Be part of a work environment where your creative ideas will be considered;
Participate in different projects that will not allow routine to set in;
Solve problems of scalability, reliability, security, etc;
Implement the latest AWS technologies;
Any other related tasks


Tech environment:

AWS
Infrastructure-as-Code (CloudFormation, CDK, etc)
Python
Typescript
CI/CD
Serverless
Docker
SaaS
Github
LaunchDarkly


What you bring to the table:

AEC, DEC or BAC in a field of study related to the position;
Minimum of 2 years of relevant experience. Whether you are a junior, intermediate or senior, we are looking for the right fit!
Excellent French, both spoken and written;
Experience with "Move Fast; Break Things" development;
Experience with the AWS environment;
Experience with collaborative development;
Experience with at least one modern programming language (Python is a plus);
Experience with IaC (infrastructure-as-code);
Knowledge of DevOps;
Knowledge of Agile/Scrum.


What we offer:

Dynamic and collaborative work environment;
Generous vacation policy upon arrival;
100% remote with access to our offices in Quebec City and Montreal if you want to;
Flextime and Flexible Fridays;
Group insurance (life, health, travel and disability insurance, prescription drug coverage, dental and more) paid in half by the employer;
Telemedicine service with Dialogue;
MacBook Pro and $750 allowance for your home office upon hire;
Tasty snacks (Fresh fruits, snacks, coffees, teas, etc.);
Referral program;
Whatever you need to keep learning and evolve professionally;
Rapid evolution in your role. Your responsibilities will not be limited!


Who we are:

Poka is an innovative application built for manufacturers to empower frontline workers to learn, solve problems and collaborate continuously from the factory floor - imagine Facebook and YouTube combined and designed for factory workers. Poka is trusted by some of the largest and most recognized global brands including Danone, Bosch, Kraft, and Johnson & Johnson. Poka has been highlighted by Gartner in three consecutive Hype Cycles as one of only ten solution providers in the Connected Worker category.

Want to learn more about our culture? Click HERE.

Qui nous sommes:

Poka est une application innovante conçue pour les fabricants afin de permettre aux travailleurs de première ligne d'apprendre, de résoudre des problèmes et de collaborer en permanence depuis l'usine - imaginez Facebook et YouTube combinés et conçus pour les travailleurs d'usine. Certaines des marques mondiales les plus importantes et les plus reconnues, dont Danone, Bosch, Kraft et Johnson & Johnson, font confiance à Poka. Poka a été mis en avant par Gartner dans trois Hype Cycles consécutifs comme l'un des dix seuls fournisseurs de solutions dans la catégorie des travailleurs connectés.

Tu veux en savoir sur notre culture? Clique ICI.
